{"tid":1502364,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"前排盾陣建議","createTime":"2019-08-24T15:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T16:07:48.000Z","uid":218158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d15aa433550849c8076de1a69ee0262125ea0e69","tid":1502364,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"我認為應該要冇空位，第一排就全長盾連住，唔好畀班狗有位入嚟，最好就貼上嗰種貼眼罩既銀色紙，噉樣入面手足唔使伸個頭出嚟都睇到班狗情況，防止突然射橡膠子彈(但要大量)，總之要令到警方睇唔到。第二排就畀啲短盾企喺道，要一隻手搭住前面。然後就隔最少3個人位企滅火隊或者遠攻手。每個人身邊要隔開最少一個身位。要有通訊兵，隨時走往前線同後排講情況，最好就係有walkie talkie，噉樣就唔使走嚟走嚟去。另外，攞長盾既唔好攞住其他武器，由短盾攞。"},{"pid":"97e5cd3106f4d56bf712f75e6355f99f88e87240","tid":1502364,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:56:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f7816523330fd651708774f52dd541b04cf93a4","tid":1502364,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:57:02.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"b66be1cc4850c2ed823107bc392303871c58594f","tid":1502364,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:57:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09e2f36895d2eee04e350556b289f7b224a2f4c4","tid":1502364,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:57:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf7d51f9f009c1563f1a187a3813b1a791f4f9a9","tid":1502364,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:57:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42a2e8a91a3285b6e5c16fd2d218ab839b4c847b","tid":1502364,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:58:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42e11776bbf1cdce6b9a0607cf79e36f44a76d1c","tid":1502364,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:58:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1fe448092100be8bee6e0998cc83f6573cacd0d","tid":1502364,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:58:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a391c004c2fb94dac73c59a34eb2db974c651b49","tid":1